{"tid":1828843,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Angelababy保護穿山甲竟與武漢肺炎扯上關係？　網民：間接劊子手","createTime":"2020-01-18T08:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T12:01:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc59430038e35f8249a6d8299d0eef5f88c3a9bd","tid":1828843,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"武漢自去年底爆發不明原因肺炎，至今疫情依然嚴重，香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良，相信新型冠狀病毒是由武漢華南海鮮批發市場出售的活野味傳人。其實中國人食野味並不是新聞，而Angelababy年多前為國際環保組織「動物救援」所拍的一個廣告宣傳片，如今就再度惹起了網民討論，有網民留言問是否在武漢取景拍攝的。<br />\n<br />\nBaby這個廣告在當時已惹起了不少爭議。在廣告中，她手抱一隻穿山甲，呼籲不要殺害食用牠們，又承諾「不用穿山甲通乳」（按：治療產後乳汁不通或缺乳的問題）。有關言論卻被質疑是「曲線」宣傳穿山甲的功效，反而會刺激更多人食用；亦有內地傳媒指出，穿山甲並沒有通乳的功效，該廣告最大問題是沒有澄清這一點。一心呼籲大家保護穿山甲的Baby更被批評是好心做壞事，有網民就指她：「無知有時也會變成間接的劊子手。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3875945/org/81ad28225a5f00df8944103203ff7913.jpg/_Fcjc3p_R7DJZ-4DOmpyC8rivvMxas7zDpNfDA6TXww\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3875945%2Forg%2F81ad28225a5f00df8944103203ff7913.jpg%2F_Fcjc3p_R7DJZ-4DOmpyC8rivvMxas7zDpNfDA6TXww&h=427a764c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3875948/org/f23eb4c1b5e23946c83a24b5b505975e.jpg/rVM24E42hPp4bNQUWE-uiQ3mXqpKXOVGlSrtz5Uq7c8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3875948%2Forg%2Ff23eb4c1b5e23946c83a24b5b505975e.jpg%2FrVM24E42hPp4bNQUWE-uiQ3mXqpKXOVGlSrtz5Uq7c8&h=7d532919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3875952/org/4b3a006fbdf77b101220158f82ec0a65.jpg/IDIimSEBpRQy47cHFsnmVKMyaCx_JyF84Vq3BOFatwQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3875952%2Forg%2F4b3a006fbdf77b101220158f82ec0a65.jpg%2FIDIimSEBpRQy47cHFsnmVKMyaCx_JyF84Vq3BOFatwQ&h=71729890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3875956/org/ec2bfa14fbfcfac9406d60408dcce8fd.jpg/KdIU_j7PwmqMzj0e